---
title: 20 oz Rib-Eye Steaks Over Risotto with Tomato Onion Jam and Freshly Cracked Peppercorns
description: Treat yourself to a real feast: this recipe comes with 20 ounces of rib-eye steaks—that’s an extra-large portion of a cut of beef known for its tenderness and rich flavor. And we haven’t stopped there with the perks: there’s also a rich, buttery risotto and a tomato onion jam that’ll blow your mind with how deliciously sweet and tangy it is. We’re even throwing in some whole peppercorns that you can grind fresh so you’ll be seasoning everything with style and flair.
